ANNED CHANGES TO IMPROVE SAFETY

FHR's policy is to pursue continuous improvement through the use of tools such as follows: 

- Continued employee process safety training;

- Improved Safe Operating Limit Repository;

- Improved Contractor onboarding process;

- Improved Reliability Operating Practices;

- Refreshed Safe Work Practice policies;

- Improved Management System Program Documents.
